DOC.brief_summary: This is a randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled, multiple-ascending dose study of MS-553 in healthy volunteers. Endpoints are safety, tolerability, and pharmacokinetics. Subjects are dosed for 14 days.
DOC.brief_title: A Multiple-Ascending Dose Study of MS-553 in Healthy Volunteers
DOC.criteria: In good general health with BMI 18 to 32 kg/m2. Females must be nonpregnant, nonlactating, postmenopausal at least 2 years or surgically sterilized at least 6 months prior History of skin rash, migraine, or clinically significant ocular diseases, conditions predisposing to QT prolongation
